<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title>Escape the Call</title>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<link href="/css/styles.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
</head>
<body>
	<header>
	</header>
	<main>
		<div id="start">
			<h1>Escape the Call</h1>
			<h2>Get off the phone with your mom!</h2>
			<p>If you can get off the phone with your mom before your time runs out, without making her furious, you get to move onto the next level!</p>
			<p>Choose the right responses to her in the right order and you just may be able to hang up the phone in time for the call not to interfere with your life!</p>
			<p>But be warned, if you hang up when your mother is angry with you, you may regret it!</p>
			<button class="start">Start the Game</button>
		</div>
		<div id="upper">
			<div id="mom-anger"></div>
			<div class="mom-phrase">
				<div id="bubble">
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div id="status">
			<div id="player-points"></div>
			<div class="current-status">
				<p>You just got home from work!</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div id="choices">
		</div>
	</main>
	<footer>
	</footer>
	<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.1.3/jquery.min.js"></script>
	<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/underscore.js/1.8.3/underscore-min.js"></script>
	<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/backbone.js/1.1.2/backbone-min.js"></script>
	<script src="/js/scripts.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
